555
00:46:51,240 --> 00:46:57,040
the app every day. So, that thing on flexibility 
though, that's almost certainly been the biggest,  

556
00:46:57,040 --> 00:47:01,440
from a mechanic perspective, the biggest DAU 
driver. One of the earliest experiments we ran  

557
00:47:01,440 --> 00:47:06,520
