00:51:00,680 --> 00:51:05,560
and then you can use those gems to buy a 
streak... And this is something we wrestle  

604
00:51:05,560 --> 00:51:10,280
with. We're actively working on an experiment, 
right now that's having a small hit to revenue,  

605
00:51:10,280 --> 00:51:14,280
but it's a really nice win for retention, 
and I think it's actually worth thinking  

