00:51:21,960 --> 00:51:26,080
the role of retention? And I think for us it 
started out much more organically, and so we  

609
00:51:26,080 --> 00:51:31,280
have a lot of monetization hooks, that again, is 
the retention PM, I would love to get rid of. But  

610
00:51:31,280 --> 00:51:36,400
again, it's sort of part of how the streak works 
right now. And so, we always have this tension of,  

611
00:51:36,400 --> 00:51:42,560
hey, if we start to make it harder to buy 
streak freezes, then fewer people buy them,  

612
00:51:42,560 --> 00:51:48,320
buy gems to buy them, and so there's this 
more convoluted series of impacts that happen.

613
00:51:48,320 --> 00:51:52,360
Yeah, no, I love that people 
wanting to buy streak freeze is  

