00:51:52,360 --> 00:51:56,520
like the ultimate sign of how much streaks matter.

615
00:51:57,040 --> 00:52:02,840
Yeah, streak freeze is the other big 
one that we've recently demonetized,  

616
00:52:02,840 --> 00:52:09,640
or introduced a free option for, is getting 
back a lost streak. So, used to lose a streak,  

617
00:52:09,640 --> 00:52:13,960
we had a feature, in the day, back in the day, 
called Streak Repair, we'd give you your streak  

618
00:52:13,960 --> 00:52:19,800
back, you had to pay gems. But what we found that 
worked way better was a feature called Earn Back,  

619
00:52:19,800 --> 00:52:23,800
and this is basically where you would have to 
do a certain number of lessons, as long as you  

620
00:52:23,800 --> 00:52:29,840
came back within a window soon after losing your 
streak, do a few lessons and we just give you your  

621
00:52:29,840 --> 00:52:35,960
streak back. And that was such a retention winner. 
And again, what we thought about was it feels like  

622
00:52:35,960 --> 00:52:41,080
you've earned it so much more when you've done... 
You deserve to have your streak back, we haven't  

