00:55:17,800 --> 00:55:21,800
23 and a half hours after you practice 
the day before. Whoa, that is a lot.

660
00:55:21,800 --> 00:55:23,360
23 and a half. Okay,

661
00:55:23,360 --> 00:55:26,360
So, basically, if you practice at noon today,  

662
00:55:26,360 --> 00:55:31,270
we'll send it to you at 11:30 
AM tomorrow, and we have done-

