00:55:31,270 --> 00:55:34,320
And it's, because it's like assuming they 
are free in that time the day before,  

664
00:55:34,320 --> 00:55:35,960
maybe they'll be free at the same time?

665
00:55:35,960 --> 00:55:42,440
And we actually moved, we used to let users set 
