01:14:31,280 --> 01:14:39,520
otherwise, you do end up in these local maximas. 
But yeah, there's still a bunch of stuff that we  

905
01:14:39,520 --> 01:14:44,800
haven't tried that I think we have high confidence 
in working out and so we'll keep doing that.

906
01:14:44,800 --> 01:14:49,880
Are there any other, say, lasting lessons 
from this journey that if someone were to  

907
01:14:49,880 --> 01:14:55,360
try to operate this way, build streaks into 
their product, anything you'd recommend?

908
01:14:55,360 --> 01:15:01,680
Yeah, I really do think it starts with... 
Streaks are an engagement hack. You can  

909
01:15:01,680 --> 01:15:06,880
make your app more retentive, I'm almost 
positive, almost every app out there can  

910
01:15:06,880 --> 01:15:12,360
make it more retentive. It is loss aversion, 
that is, again, armchair psychologist Jackson,  

911
01:15:13,160 --> 01:15:22,160
it's just a thing that works on humans. But 
if your app is not something that users want  

912
01:15:22,160 --> 01:15:27,480
to use every day, or whatever cadence 
you want your app to be, to work on,  

913
01:15:27,480 --> 01:15:30,800
it's going to be, you're only going to get 
so much from that streak, and honestly,  

914
01:15:30,800 --> 01:15:34,320
it's probably going to distract you from what 
really should matter, which is making your app  

915
01:15:34,320 --> 01:15:38,160
something that people want to use every day.
And so, if you start focusing on the streak but  

916
01:15:38,160 --> 01:15:43,280
you haven't made that an enjoyable experience, 
you're just going to waste a lot of time,  

917
01:15:43,280 --> 01:15:46,720
honestly. And so, I think making sure that you 
have your core loop of your app figured out,  

918
01:15:46,720 --> 01:15:51,520
that it is giving value to users, it is something 
that they want to come back to every day,  

919
01:15:51,520 --> 01:15:57,320
that really sets the stage for something to 
layer a streak on. So, resist the temptation,  

920
01:15:58,120 --> 01:16:03,280
if you don't think you've reached that point, 
to go too hard down the path of streak.

921
01:16:03,280 --> 01:16:05,720
That's a really good point. Just like 
a streak is not going to solve your  

922
01:16:05,720 --> 01:16:09,480
problems if people don't actually care 
about the core value you're providing.

923
01:16:09,480 --> 01:16:13,240
No, and honestly, it'll probably cause more 
problems if what you end up focusing on is  

924
01:16:13,240 --> 01:16:19,760
how do I make the streak highly engaging, but 
your app is... You're wasting time that could  

925
01:16:19,760 --> 01:16:26,480
otherwise be better spent on solving more 
