is because you care about your streaks much." You  

929
01:16:42,920 --> 01:16:46,760
being Duolingo. The reason why users care about 
our streak so much is because Duolingo cares about  

930
01:16:46,760 --> 01:16:50,080
the streaks so much. And we're like, what do you 
mean? Well, he's like, well, after every session  

931
01:16:50,080 --> 01:16:54,000
you see a big streak screen, and it's animated 
