938
01:17:22,600 --> 01:17:28,120
because we want it to be top of mind for users. 
And that's not by accident then that users start  

939
01:17:28,120 --> 01:17:32,080
to care about it. And so, I think just as you're 
thinking about building the streak, making sure  

940
01:17:32,080 --> 01:17:35,440
that you're giving it the visibility it deserves, 
if you want it to have the kind of impact that  

941
01:17:35,440 --> 01:17:42,640
Duolingo has, it's sort of an important hierarchy 
principle to think about as you design things.

