01:17:58,800 --> 01:18:05,840
Maybe final thing is, look, we ran so many 
tests on our Duolingo streak to figure out  

947
01:18:05,840 --> 01:18:12,000
what worked. We have a philosophy at Duolingo, 
of test it first. We are a lot of times willing  

948
01:18:12,000 --> 01:18:16,040
to test things. I really think that if you're 
going to try to introduce a streak, or you want  

949
01:18:16,040 --> 01:18:24,480
to improve on the streak you have, don't get 
too caught up in the philosophy of everything,  

